exploratory_workflow.query: SELECT ?s ?p ?pname WHERE { ?s wdt:P106/wdt:P279* wd:Q82955 ; wdt:P27 ?c ; ?p ?o . ?c wdt:P463 wd:Q458 . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pname . FILTER NOT EXISTS {?s wdt:P570 ?d} . } LIMIT 10

SELECT (COUNT (?s) as ?numberPoliticians) ?country WHERE { ?s wdt:P106/wdt:P279* wd:Q82955 ; wdt:P27 ?c . ?c wdt:P463 wd:Q458 . ?c <http://schema.org/name> ?country . FILTER NOT EXISTS {?s wdt:P570 ?d} . } GROUP BY ?country ORDER BY desc (?numberPoliticians) LIMIT 10

SELECT ?s ?politician ?country WHERE { ?s wdt:P106/wdt:P279* wd:Q82955 ; wdt:P27 ?c1 ; wdt:P27 ?c2 . ?c1 wdt:P463 wd:Q458 . ?s <http://schema.org/name> ?politician . ?c1 <http://schema.org/name> ?country1 . ?c2 <http://schema.org/name> ?country2 . FILTER NOT EXISTS {?s wdt:P570 ?d} . FILTER (?c1 != ?c2) } LIMIT 10

SELECT ( COUNT (?sname) as ?number) ?oname { ?s wdt:P106/wdt:P279* wd:Q82955 ; wdt:P106 ?o ; wdt:P27 ?c . ?s <http://schema.org/name> ?sname . ?o <http://schema.org/name> ?oname . FILTER ((?c = wd:Q38) || (?c = wd:Q142)) . } GROUP BY ?oname ORDER BY desc (?number) LIMIT 4

SELECT ( COUNT (?sname) as ?number) ?oname { ?s wdt:P106/wdt:P279* wd:Q82955 ; wdt:P106 ?o ; wdt:P27 ?c . ?s <http://schema.org/name> ?sname . ?o <http://schema.org/name> ?oname . FILTER ((?c = wd:Q38) || (?c = wd:Q142)) . FILTER NOT EXISTS {?s wdt:P570 ?d} . } GROUP BY ?oname ORDER BY desc (?number) LIMIT 4
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pname { ?s wdt:P31 wd:Q5 ; ?p ?sp . ?sp wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . ?s <http://schema.org/name> ?sname . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pname . } LIMIT 10

SELECT (COUNT (?s) AS ?numberPolitician) ?cname { ?s wdt:P106 wd:Q82955 ; wdt:P26 ?sp ; wdt:P27 ?c . ?sp wdt:P106 wd:Q82955 . ?c wdt:P463 wd:Q458 . ?c <http://schema.org/name> ?cname . } GROUP BY ?cname ORDER BY desc(?numberPolitician) LIMIT 10
